into the theme today, which

00:10:45.000 --> 00:10:47.820
is empowering kids through
sports and, really, just

00:10:47.820 --> 00:10:48.872
in general.

00:10:48.872 --> 00:10:50.830
So let's talk a little
about your photo series.

